The advent of online payment systems has significantly facilitated the payment process. However, it has also led to a surge in payment fraud incidents. Instances of online payment fraud can occur with any individual utilizing various payment systems, particularly during credit card transactions. Consequently, identifying online payment fraud becomes crucial for credit card companies to safeguard customers from unauthorized charges for goods and services they did not acquire. This code is tailored for you if you want to develop the skills to detect online payment fraud. Within this code, I will guide you through detecting online payment fraud using machine learning and Python.
